./gradlew clean build -Dorg.gradle.debug=true -Dkotlin.daemon.jvm.options="-Xdebug,-Xrunjdwp:transport=dt_socket\,address=5005\,server=y\,suspend=n"

Plan B (if the first line doesn't work for a reason):

./gradlew clean build --no-daemon -Dorg.gradle.debug=true -Dkotlin.compiler.execution.strategy=in-process

